long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Finding candidates and building recruiting pipelines is quite the task! With Model Match Sourcing Extension for Chrome, you can source contacts and build pipelines quickly without switching back and forth between apps. Handle all of the organization right from the extension by Tagging and Assigning contacts and source all the information you and your team need to make contact like phone numbers, emails, social media links, and more. Level up your talent acquisition efforts with a single click.
